<Callout type="tip" title="Buy once, buy right">
  A professional multimeter from an established manufacturer — one that carries genuine CAT ratings, certified True RMS measurement, and robust test lead assembly — will outlast several cycles of cheap replacements. The true cost of an entry-level instrument includes the cost of wrong readings, undetected faults, and eventual replacement. For an instrument you will use every working day, investing in quality pays for itself quickly.
</Callout>

